These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
House: art-deco, modern, tower, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the modern house##1
6. the tower house is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| House      | gothic-revival  | art-deco | modern  | tower |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea, cola
1. the egyptian is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking cola##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Beverage           | tea      | almond-milk    | iced-tea | cola      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, havana, dannemann, aristoff
1. the person eating corn is the havana-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Cigar   | havana  | aristoff   | dannemann | tiparillo    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lilac, aquamarine, turquise
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes lilac##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
5. the person who likes turquise is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Color   | turquise   | aquamarine     | lilac    | brown       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, project-manager, analyst, coach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the coach is on the left or right of the analyst##3
3. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
6. the coach is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Job          | analyst | coach   | lawyer   | project-manager    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

