.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, july, march
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the police-officer and the person who's birthday is in july##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Birthday   | july        | march     | november       | january   |

