.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
House: palace, modern, victorian, tower
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, snake, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is the tower house##1
2. the palace house is between the modern house and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
5. the palace house is in an even position##4
6. the victorian house is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| House   | modern | palace  | victorian  | tower   |
| Pet           | turtle  | goldfish | snake | hamster |

