.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Birthday    | july | september  | may | november |

