.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, collecting, skydiving
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | skydiving | video-games | collecting |

