.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, fishing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, electronic, salsa, country
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the fan of salsa is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
5. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan of funk##5
6. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | funk | salsa  | country |

