.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
House: futuristic, tower, wooden, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the farmhouse house is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the wooden house##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the tower house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| House         | wooden  | farmhouse | futuristic | tower |

