The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, november, september
1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
