.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, azure, pink
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the person who likes azure##1
5. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color   | pink  | aquamarine | lilac | azure |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

