.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey, weightlifting, biathlon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Sport      | snowboarding   | weightlifting  | ice-hockey      | biathlon       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

