.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, italian, thai, turkish
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, baking, rock-climbing
1. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
2. the thai is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the german##5
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german     | italian | turkish | thai |
| Hobby     | singing | card-games    | baking    | rock-climbing |

