.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, goat, rat
1. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
3. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Pet   | goat | rat  | ferret | bird        |

